snippet.title: A Collection Of Bad Moments - Trailer
snippet.description:
A Collection of Bad Moments is an adventure game where the player discovers themselves in various tough situations and must use their wits to figure a way out! The moment vary from asteroid mission and virtual reality to air ship duel!

The adventure game will be published on Steam!
